description: Queen is one of the most successful and beloved bands of all time. You know their music, now learn about all about the band! Did you know Freddie Mercury was crazy about cats? Or that Brian May has a doctorate degree in astrophysics? Ask Queen Facts for a random Queen fact and learn something new about one of your favorite bands.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Queen Facts to tell me a Queen fact
Alexa, ask Queen Facts to tell me more about Queen
name: Queen Facts
shortDescription: Learn about one of the world's greatest bands, Queen, one fact at a time.
